-- Mauritania Names Camara As Finance Minister, Replacing Moulaye, AMI Says
-- B y   O u d a a   M a r o u f
-- 2010-12-16T10:11:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/mauritania-names-camara-as-finance-minister-replacing-moulaye-ami-says.html
Mauritania named Amedi Camara
finance minister, replacing Ahmed Ould Moulaye who will take a
position in the president’s office, according to the state-owned
Agence Mauritanienne d’Information.  Camara was previously the general secretary of the Industry
and Mines Ministry in the northwest African nation.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  